'''Krobus''' is the only friendly [[Monsters|monster]] players will encounter, however he still refers to other hostile monsters as his friends. He is a shadow person who lives in [[the Sewers]]. He sells a variety of rare goods. He is also available as a [[#Roommate|roommate]].

==Schedule==
Krobus can always be found in the Sewers once [[the Player]] obtains the [[Rusty Key]].

==Shop==
Krobus' Shop is open all hours every day, even [[Festivals|festival]] days.

