==Relationships==
Krobus is almost never seen outside interacting with other [[villagers]]. He dislikes [[Dwarf|dwarves]], stating that a 1,000 year [[Setting#The Elemental Wars|war]] between the dwarves and his people recently ended. He believes if the dwarves knew where he was, they'd send an assassin.

The [[Wizard]] is aware of his presence and [[Dwarf#Heart Events|intervenes]] to prevent conflicts.

